<node id="Mi Home">
  <data key="d0">Mi Home</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Mi Home is Xiaomi's offline retail store chain launched as part of its New Retail strategy. It uses a "high-frequency帶動low-frequency" approach, selling products like fitness bands, earphones, and power strips to drive traffic for higher-ticket items like phones.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3d53115d4331a6108b6e778bee3c915f</data>
