  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">Mi 10 Series is Xiaomi's premium smartphone lineup launched in 2020, successfully entering the 4,000+ yuan price range and marking a breakthrough in Xiaomi's premiumization strategy.</data>
