  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Xiao Ai is Xiaomi's AI voice assistant that connects smart devices including TVs, speakers, routers, and robot vacuums as part of Xiaomi's "AIoT" (Artificial Intelligence of Things) strategy.</data>
