<node id="Ironman Three">
  <data key="d0">Ironman Three</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Ironman Three is Xiaomi Company's unique business model comprising three core components: hardware, new retail, and internet services. Hardware focuses on extreme cost-performance without relying on hardware profits; New Retail includes integrated online-offline channels like Mi Mall and Mi Home; Internet Services include MIUI ads, app stores, cloud services, and games.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3d53115d4331a6108b6e778bee3c915f</data>
